{"id":15078,"date":"2024-04-08T17:57:51","date_gmt":"2024-04-08T10:57:51","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/?p=15078"},"modified":"2024-04-08T17:57:52","modified_gmt":"2024-04-08T10:57:52","slug":"hyundai-thanh-cong-trien-khai-chuong-trinh-uu-dai-thang-4-cho-khach-hang","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/hyundai-thanh-cong-trien-khai-chuong-trinh-uu-dai-thang-4-cho-khach-hang\/","title":{"rendered":"Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng tri\u1ec3n khai ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i th\u00e1ng 4 cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>T\u1eeb nay cho \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft 30\/04\/2024, Li\u00ean doanh \u00f4 t\u00f4 Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam (HTV) ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tri\u1ec3n khai ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u201cM\u1eebng \u0110\u1ea1i l\u1ec5 &#8211; R\u01b0\u1edbc x\u1ebf Hyundai\u201d \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea1i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0110\u1ea1i l\u00fd tr\u00ean to\u00e0n qu\u1ed1c.<\/p>\n<p>B\u01b0\u1edbc sang Qu\u00fd II n\u0103m 2024 v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n b\u1ee9t ph\u00e1 c\u1ee7a n\u1ec1n kinh t\u1ebf n\u00f3i chung, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u00f4 t\u00f4 n\u00f3i ri\u00eang, HTV cam k\u1ebft s\u1ebd n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng ngh\u1ec9, \u0111\u1ec3 mang \u0111\u1ebfn cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u00eau d\u00f9ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u00f4 t\u00f4 b\u1ec1n b\u1ec9, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, uy t\u00edn.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/hyundai-thanh-cong-trien-khai-chuong-trinh-uu-dai-thang-4-cho-khach-hang\/khuyen-mai-thang-4_1200x628\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-15080\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-15080\" src=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/khuyen-mai-thang-4_1200x628-1024x536.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1110\" height=\"581\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/khuyen-mai-thang-4_1200x628-1024x536.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/khuyen-mai-thang-4_1200x628-300x157.jpg 300w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/khuyen-mai-thang-4_1200x628-768x402.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/khuyen-mai-thang-4_1200x628-1536x804.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/khuyen-mai-thang-4_1200x628-2048x1072.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1110px) 100vw, 1110px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>Th\u00e1ng 4 n\u00e0y, v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh c\u00f9ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u00eau d\u00f9ng c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi s\u1edf h\u1eefu chi\u1ebfc xe ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p, ti\u1ec7n nghi v\u00e0 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i cho c\u1ea3 gia \u0111\u00ecnh c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh du l\u1ecbch kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 nh\u00e2n d\u1ecbp ngh\u1ec9 \u0110\u1ea1i l\u1ec5 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 m\u00f9a h\u00e8 s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ebfn, HTV ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tri\u1ec3n khai ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u201cM\u1eebng \u0110\u1ea1i l\u1ec5 &#8211; R\u01b0\u1edbc x\u1ebf Hyundai\u201d \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft ng\u00e0y 30\/04\/2024 t\u1ea1i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00fd \u1ee7y quy\u1ec1n Hyundai tr\u00ean to\u00e0n qu\u1ed1c.<\/p>\n<p>Theo \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u01b0\u1edfng 1 trong 2 g\u00f3i \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho c\u00e1c xe Custin, Elantra, Accent v\u00e0 Grand i10 nh\u01b0 sau:<\/p>\n<p>&#8211;\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 G\u00f3i 1: \u01afu \u0111\u00e3i l\u00e3i su\u1ea5t tr\u1ea3 g\u00f3p ch\u1ec9 t\u1eeb 0% trong 12 th\u00e1ng (\u00c2n h\u1ea1n n\u1ee3 g\u1ed1c l\u00ean t\u1edbi 9 th\u00e1ng t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c t\u1eebng ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng)<\/p>\n<p>&#8211;\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 G\u00f3i 2: G\u00f3i h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh l\u00ean t\u1edbi 50% L\u1ec7 ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1<\/p>\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i ra, Kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng mua Grand i10 c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eb7ng 1 n\u0103m B\u1ea3o hi\u1ec3m v\u1eadt ch\u1ea5t PJICO ho\u1eb7c BSH trong th\u1eddi gian n\u00e0y.<\/p>\n<p>Trong \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c m\u1ee9c l\u00e3i su\u1ea5t \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i khi mua c\u00e1c xe n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng n\u1ebfu kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng vay mua xe t\u1ea1i Ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i c\u1ed5 ph\u1ea7n Ngo\u1ea1i th\u01b0\u01a1ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam (VCB), Ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng Th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i c\u1ed5 ph\u1ea7n Qu\u1ed1c T\u1ebf Vi\u1ec7t Nam (VIB),\u00a0\u00a0Ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng TMCP Th\u1ecbnh V\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 Ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n (PG Bank)\u00a0v\u00e0\u00a0Ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng Th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i c\u1ed5 ph\u1ea7n Vi\u1ec7t Nam Th\u1ecbnh V\u01b0\u1ee3ng (VPB).<\/p>\n<p>HTV c\u00f2n ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u0110\u1ea1i l\u00fd tri\u1ec3n khai ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh khuy\u1ebfn m\u1ea1i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng cho Hyundai Santa Fe v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 nh\u01b0 sau:<\/p>\n<figure class=\"table\">\n<table style=\"height: 435px;\" width=\"1268\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>STT<\/strong><\/td>\n<td><strong>Phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n<\/strong><\/td>\n<td><strong>M\u1ee9c khuy\u1ebfn m\u1ea1i (VND)<\/strong><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>1<\/td>\n<td>Santa Fe 2.5 X\u0103ng<\/td>\n<td>50.000.000<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2<\/td>\n<td>Santa Fe 2.5 X\u0103ng Cao c\u1ea5p<\/td>\n<td>75.000.000<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3<\/td>\n<td>Santa Fe 2.2 D\u1ea7u<\/td>\n<td>50.000.000<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4<\/td>\n<td>Santa Fe 2.2 D\u1ea7u Cao c\u1ea5p<\/td>\n<td>50.000.000<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5<\/td>\n<td>Santa Fe Hybrid<\/td>\n<td>100.000.000<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<\/figure>\n<figure class=\"image\"><img decoding=\"async\" title=\"Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam (HTV)\" src=\"https:\/\/hyundai-api.thanhcong.vn\/storage\/uploads\/editors\/2024\/04\/02\/Hyundai%20SantaFe-Aug2023.jpg\" alt=\"Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam (HTV)\" \/><\/figure>\n<p>B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, nhi\u1ec1u m\u1eabu xe kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng c\u00f3 c\u00e1c g\u00f3i \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i ri\u00eang t\u1eeb HTV v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ea1i l\u00fd.<\/p>\n<p>Kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng vui l\u00f2ng li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0110\u1ea1i l\u00fd g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft th\u00f4ng tin chi ti\u1ebft v\u1ec1 ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>T\u1eeb nay cho \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft 30\/04\/2024, Li\u00ean doanh \u00f4 t\u00f4 Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam (HTV) ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tri\u1ec3n khai ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u201cM\u1eebng \u0110\u1ea1i l\u1ec5 &#8211; R\u01b0\u1edbc x\u1ebf Hyundai\u201d \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea1i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0110\u1ea1i l\u00fd tr\u00ean to\u00e0n qu\u1ed1c. B\u01b0\u1edbc sang Qu\u00fd II n\u0103m 2024 v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":15080,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"yst_prominent_words":[],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/15078"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author